<body>

   

    <div class="recipe-container">
        <h1>Crispy & Tasty Dosa Recipe</h1>
       

        <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
        <ul class="ingredients-list">
            <li>2 cups Dosa Rice</li>
            <li>1/2 cup Urad Dal (Black Gram Lentils)</li>
            <li>1/4 tsp Fenugreek Seeds</li>
            <li>Salt to taste</li>
            <li>Water as needed</li>
            <li>Oil or Ghee for cooking</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Instructions:</h2>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Soak rice, urad dal, and fenugreek seeds separately for 6 hours.</li>
            <li>Grind urad dal until smooth and then grind rice to a slightly coarse texture.</li>
            <li>Mix both batters, add salt, and ferment overnight.</li>
            <li>Heat a tawa, pour a ladle of batter, and spread it thin.</li>
            <li>Drizzle oil or ghee around the dosa and cook until golden brown.</li>
            <li>Serve hot with coconut chutney and sambar.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

</body>
